---
import '../styles.css'
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Super · 文档</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="https://websource-meiyi.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/website/super/logo.ico" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="layout">
      <section class="hero">
        <p class="kicker">SUPER DOCS</p>
        <h1>Super 云工作区文档</h1>
        <p class="desc">了解 Super 的平台架构、API 接口和开发指南。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="cards">
        <a href="/docs/architecture" class="card">
          <h3>平台架构</h3>
          <p>了解 Super 的整体架构设计、路由策略和数据模型。</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/docs/api" class="card">
          <h3>API 参考</h3>
          <p>查看完整的 REST API 接口文档，涵盖认证、资产、画布、计费等全部模块。</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/docs/development" class="card">
          <h3>开发指南</h3>
          <p>本地开发环境搭建、项目结构和贡献流程。</p>
        </a>
      </section>

      <section class="api-quick">
        <h2>API 快速入口</h2>
        <div class="api-grid">
          <a href="/docs/api/authentication" class="api-link">认证</a>
          <a href="/docs/api/assets" class="api-link">资产管理</a>
          <a href="/docs/api/canvas" class="api-link">画布生成</a>
          <a href="/docs/api/tasks" class="api-link">任务中心</a>
          <a href="/docs/api/records" class="api-link">生成记录</a>
          <a href="/docs/api/billing" class="api-link">计费与余额</a>
          <a href="/docs/api/notifications" class="api-link">通知系统</a>
          <a href="/docs/api/models" class="api-link">模型目录</a>
          <a href="/docs/api/gateway" class="api-link">OpenAI 网关</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Super. Built with Astro.</p>
      </footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .api-quick { margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .api-quick h2 {
    font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #e5e5e5;
    margin: 0 0 16px; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .api-grid {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px;
  }
  .api-link {
    display: inline-block; padding: 6px 14px;
    border: 1px solid #2a2a2a; border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 13px; color: #aaa; text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.12s;
  }
  .api-link:hover {
    border-color: #3a3a3a; color: #e5e5e5; background: #1c1c1c;
  }
</style>
